6)  Projects Section (With Dates & Names & Proof)

• Smart Room Automation (Aug 2025 – Nov 2025)
Developed an ESP-based smart room system using MQTT, touch interfaces, and custom Fusion 360 enclosures for automated lighting and appliances.

• Customized Voice Assistant — LLM-Free (Sep 2025 – Oct 2025)
Built an offline Raspberry Pi–based voice assistant with wake-word detection, speech recognition, lightweight NLP, and MQTT-powered home control.

• Drone Without Flight Controller (May 2025 – Jun 2025)
Designed a drone controlled entirely via Raspberry Pi 4, implementing motor control, stabilization logic, and ROS-based internal communication.

• Wi-Fi & Bluetooth Jammer (Feb 2025 – Mar 2025)
Created an ESP32 + NRF24 frequency-hopping jammer with configurable modes for wireless interference testing.

• Voice-Controlled Robotic Arm (4-DOF) (Nov 2024 – Dec 2024)
Built a 4-DOF robotic arm with Bluetooth voice commands, ROS communication, and basic actuator control for simple kinematic operations.

